287
00:12:05,980 --> 00:12:06,850
After death,

288
00:12:06,880 --> 00:12:08,330
the body was hung from the ceiling beam.

289
00:12:08,330 --> 00:12:09,700
As for who did this,

290
00:12:09,720 --> 00:12:11,650
further investigation is needed.

291
00:12:12,230 --> 00:12:13,160
Your Highness,

292
00:12:13,870 --> 00:12:16,120
why were you
in the lady scholar's room?

293
00:12:16,320 --> 00:12:17,010
Lord Feng,

294
00:12:17,090 --> 00:12:18,290
to be honest with you,

295
00:12:18,440 --> 00:12:19,840
at the Imperial Banquet,

296
00:12:19,890 --> 00:12:20,820
my maid Wan

297
00:12:20,850 --> 00:12:21,940
received a note.

298
00:12:23,050 --> 00:12:24,880
It said that the lady scholar

299
00:12:24,910 --> 00:12:25,250
wanted to meet me in her room at 9 p.m.,

300
00:12:25,250 --> 00:12:26,700
[Critical issue regarding exam fraud.
Meet at my room at 9 p.m.]

301
00:12:26,700 --> 00:12:28,370
to discuss something critical.

302
00:12:28,370 --> 00:12:29,800
I disguised myself as a scholar

303
00:12:29,800 --> 00:12:31,720
and went to the Imperial Academy at 9 p.m.

304
00:12:31,720 --> 00:12:33,380
I noticed shadows moving inside the room,

305
00:12:33,380 --> 00:12:34,780
so I immediately entered

306
00:12:37,470 --> 00:12:38,310
[Hall of True Writings]

307
00:12:40,050 --> 00:12:41,910
and found the lady hanging there.

308
00:12:46,960 --> 00:12:47,630
Help!

309
00:12:47,840 --> 00:12:49,320
Somebody, help!

310
00:12:59,000 --> 00:13:00,090
I found

311
00:13:00,160 --> 00:13:02,420
animal fur and scratch marks in the room,

312
00:13:04,300 --> 00:13:06,630
as well as an inkstone stained with blood.

313
00:13:12,750 --> 00:13:14,520
Murder! Murder!

314
00:13:16,300 --> 00:13:17,080
I'm confused too.

315
00:13:17,080 --> 00:13:18,610
She was fine at the banquet.

316
00:13:19,120 --> 00:13:22,000
