right after returning?

317
00:13:22,000 --> 00:13:22,510
My lord,

318
00:13:23,040 --> 00:13:24,770
please take a look at this note.

319
00:13:26,360 --> 00:13:27,030
These are the three
proposed exam questions.

320
00:13:27,030 --> 00:13:29,110
[On ruling with reward and trust.]

321
00:13:29,110 --> 00:13:29,770
They should have

322
00:13:29,770 --> 00:13:30,410
[The founding Emperor
won Wu by ruling alone.]

323
00:13:30,430 --> 00:13:30,670
[The last Emperor fell by ruling alone.]

324
00:13:30,670 --> 00:13:31,030
been presented to His Majesty

325
00:13:31,030 --> 00:13:31,310
[Same act, yet opposite results—why?]

326
00:13:31,910 --> 00:13:34,230
the day before the test
for him to choose one.

327
00:13:34,230 --> 00:13:35,150
Why were these three questions

328
00:13:35,150 --> 00:13:36,960
found in Lu Yueying's room?

329
00:13:37,970 --> 00:13:41,170
This matter must be reported
to His Majesty immediately.

330
00:13:43,070 --> 00:13:43,930
Your Highness,

331
00:13:44,210 --> 00:13:45,690
forgive me, but I must fulfill my duty.

332
00:13:45,690 --> 00:13:47,330
You were found at the scene,

333
00:13:47,440 --> 00:13:48,810
holding a weapon,

334
00:13:48,870 --> 00:13:50,320
which makes you a major suspect.

335
00:13:50,320 --> 00:13:53,740
You must come with me to the Court of
Judicial Review for investigation.

336
00:13:53,740 --> 00:13:55,510
Do your duty, Lord Feng.

337
00:13:55,720 --> 00:13:56,280
Please.

338
00:14:02,760 --> 00:14:05,100
[Court of Judicial Review]

339
00:14:10,750 --> 00:14:12,150
-Your Majesty.
-At ease.

340
00:14:14,810 --> 00:14:17,120
Leaving the palace without permission
and getting involved in a murder case,

341
00:14:17,120 --> 00:14:18,450
what exactly happened?

342
00:14:22,840 --> 00:14:24,320
It was my misjudgment.

343
00:14:27,630 --> 00:14:28,440
But I was concerned that

344
00:14:28,440 --> 00:14:30,100
if there truly was exam fraud,

345
00:14:30,770 --> 00:14:31,600
it could

346
00:14:31,920 --> 00:14:33,620
shake the court itself.

347
00:14:35,150 --> 00:14:36,500
Right now, you're the prime suspect

348
00:14:36,500 --> 00:14:38,440
in the murder of the third-ranked scholar.

349
00:14:38,440 --> 00:14:40,440
Aren't you worried about yourself?

350
00:14:45,900 --> 00:14:47,830
The innocent have nothing to fear.

351
00:14:47,940 --> 00:14:48,940
I am not worried.

352
00:14:54,320 --> 00:14:56,380
If someone deliberately frames you,

353
00:14:56,550 --> 00:14:58,480
