354
00:14:58,610 --> 00:14:59,970
and even if you escape the quagmire,

355
00:14:59,970 --> 00:15:01,900
you'll still be stained by the mud.

356
00:15:07,170 --> 00:15:09,080
I believe justice will prevail,

357
00:15:10,450 --> 00:15:11,980
and I trust in Your Majesty.

358
00:15:23,660 --> 00:15:24,300
[Leyu,]

359
00:15:24,990 --> 00:15:25,920
[I believe you,]

360
00:15:26,370 --> 00:15:28,430
[and I will protect you completely.]

361
00:15:33,930 --> 00:15:38,630
[Ningzheng Hall]

362
00:15:38,630 --> 00:15:39,570
The case of Lu Yueying's hanging.

363
00:15:39,570 --> 00:15:40,200
[Report]

364
00:15:40,200 --> 00:15:42,120
With both witness testimony
and physical evidence,

365
00:15:42,120 --> 00:15:44,950
Lord Feng still
insists on further investigation,

366
00:15:44,950 --> 00:15:47,000
are you trying to shield someone?

367
00:15:52,170 --> 00:15:52,930
Lord Wang,

368
00:15:53,550 --> 00:15:55,430
as a royal consort,

369
00:15:55,510 --> 00:15:57,440
why would Consort Su harm Lu Yueying?

370
00:15:57,440 --> 00:15:59,100
Even if she wanted to harm her—

371
00:15:59,150 --> 00:16:01,280
Consort Su's skilled in martial arts,

372
00:16:01,320 --> 00:16:02,520
there were countless

373
00:16:02,700 --> 00:16:03,820
ways to do it.

374
00:16:04,390 --> 00:16:06,250
Why would she need that inkstone?

375
00:16:07,790 --> 00:16:08,590
Your Majesty,

376
00:16:08,870 --> 00:16:11,270
I believe there are still
many doubts in this case.

377
00:16:11,270 --> 00:16:12,550
It cannot be closed yet.

378
00:16:12,550 --> 00:16:13,340
Lord Feng,

379
00:16:13,480 --> 00:16:15,680
you're clearly favoring the Su family.

380
00:16:15,790 --> 00:16:16,790
Could it be

381
00:16:17,190 --> 00:16:19,240
you're forming factions for personal gain?

382
00:16:19,240 --> 00:16:20,210
Nonsense!

383
00:16:21,160 --> 00:16:21,960
Your Majesty,

384
00:16:22,200 --> 00:16:23,720
this case involves my sister,

385
00:16:23,720 --> 00:16:25,250
and I should recuse myself.

386
00:16:25,270 --> 00:16:27,170
But Lord Wang speaks with such certainty—

387
00:16:27,170 --> 00:16:28,570
I cannot agree.

388
00:16:29,000 --> 00:16:29,790
The Su family

389
00:16:30,030 --> 00:16:31,390
has always been loyal

390
00:16:31,640 --> 00:16:32,790
and dutiful,

391
00:16:33,080 --> 00:16:35,140
and would never commit illegal acts.

392
00:16:35,580 --> 00:16:36,510
I believe

393
00:16:36,720 --> 00:16:38,320
the innocent will be proven so.

394
00:16:38,320 --> 00:16:39,450
Your Majesty is wise

395
00:16:39,910 --> 00:16:41,770
and will surely uncover the truth

396
00:16:41,790 --> 00:16:43,520
to clear my family's name.

397
00:16:45,680 --> 00:16:46,340
Your Majesty,

398
00:16:46,340 --> 00:16:47,600
regardless of whether Lord Feng

399
00:16:47,600 --> 00:16:49,790
has close ties with the Su family,

400
00:16:50,000 --> 00:16:51,600
his judgment

401
00:16:51,600 --> 00:16:53,060
is likely already biased.

402
00:16:53,090 --> 00:16:55,100
I'm afraid he'll lose his impartiality

403
00:16:55,100 --> 00:16:56,870
when investigating this case. I—

404
00:16:56,870 --> 00:16:57,550
Enough.

405
00:17:00,480 --> 00:17:02,200
Whether it's the Court of Judicial Review

406
00:17:02,200 --> 00:17:03,690
or the Ministry of Justice,

407
00:17:03,690 --> 00:17:05,390
I can no longer trust

408
00:17:05,630 --> 00:17:07,960
either of you for future investigations.

409
00:17:08,750 --> 00:17:09,750
Grand Preceptor,

410
00:17:10,790 --> 00:17:13,440
Yin Cong has been
guarding the imperial tomb for a year

411
00:17:13,440 --> 00:17:15,260
and will soon return to report her duties.

412
00:17:15,260 --> 00:17:16,619
She's upright in character,

413
00:17:16,619 --> 00:17:18,470
both a royal relative
and from a noble family,

414
00:17:18,470 --> 00:17:20,470
and helped solve the Xi Zimo case.

415
00:17:21,230 --> 00:17:22,619
I want to summon her back

416
00:17:22,960 --> 00:17:24,420
to lead the Justice Bureau

417
00:17:24,579 --> 00:17:26,109
and investigate this case.

418
00:17:26,819 --> 00:17:28,020
Your Majesty is wise.

419
00:17:29,070 --> 00:17:30,590
Your Majesty is wise.

420
00:17:34,210 --> 00:17:36,940
[Grand Preceptor's Mansion]

421
00:17:37,740 --> 00:17:38,710
Grand Preceptor,

422
00:17:38,710 --> 00:17:40,120
it seems His Majesty

423
00:17:40,550 --> 00:17:42,410
is determined to protect Su Leyu.

424
00:17:45,000 --> 00:17:46,480
Even fish in a tank

425
00:17:46,900 --> 00:17:48,190
sometimes need

426
00:17:48,860 --> 00:17:50,680
different feed.

427
00:17:53,150 --> 00:17:56,740
[Court of Judicial Review]

428
00:17:56,740 --> 00:17:58,830
So this matter isn't simple.

429
00:17:59,300 --> 00:18:01,160
They're targeting our Su family.

430
00:18:01,780 --> 00:18:03,210
You must be very careful.

431
00:18:03,550 --> 00:18:04,200
Brother,

432
00:18:04,400 --> 00:18:05,350
don't worry.

433
00:18:05,520 --> 00:18:07,510
The Court of Judicial Review
has always been fair

434
00:18:07,510 --> 00:18:09,240
and won't mistreat prisoners.

435
00:18:10,160 --> 00:18:11,220
I'll be going then.

436
00:19:11,330 --> 00:19:12,440
[Ever-growing Radiance]

437
00:19:12,440 --> 00:19:13,900
Greetings, Your Majesty.

438
00:19:14,320 --> 00:19:16,120
Have you assumed your position?

439
00:19:16,500 --> 00:19:17,110
Yes.

440
00:19:18,510 --> 00:19:20,660
I came to thank Your Majesty
for this honor.

441
00:19:20,660 --> 00:19:23,150
I thought I'd guard
the imperial tombs all my life.

442
00:19:23,150 --> 00:19:24,090
Never expecting

443
00:19:24,610 --> 00:19:26,210
I could serve at court again.

444
00:19:28,490 --> 00:19:30,900
I know you and Leyu
share a deep friendship.

445
00:19:31,350 --> 00:19:32,870
You once earnestly advised her,

446
00:19:32,870 --> 00:19:34,930
which shows your upright character.

447
00:19:35,060 --> 00:19:35,710
Moreover,

448
00:19:37,070 --> 00:19:38,720
when I married Consort Su,

449
00:19:39,380 --> 00:19:41,710
you presented me with a significant gift.

450
00:19:43,700 --> 00:19:44,920
I dare not presume Your Majesty's

451
00:19:44,920 --> 00:19:45,720
deep meaning,

452
00:19:46,530 --> 00:19:48,930
but since you've granted me this position,

453
00:19:49,040 --> 00:19:52,070
