00:20:21,010 --> 00:20:23,600
while food was served, then escaped.

462
00:20:43,720 --> 00:20:44,650
[Taiji Palace]

463
00:20:44,650 --> 00:20:47,130
Your Majesty, Consort Su's escape

464
00:20:47,210 --> 00:20:48,600
