handed over to the Justice Bureau.

483
00:21:26,070 --> 00:21:27,000
Lord Yin,

484
00:21:27,970 --> 00:21:29,170
what's your opinion?

485
00:21:30,190 --> 00:21:31,110
Your Majesty,

486
00:21:31,330 --> 00:21:32,540
this case is riddled with doubts.

487
00:21:32,540 --> 00:21:34,120
